				ABOUT

dsbmc-cli is a simple command-line client for DSBMD. It's basically a test for
libdsbmc.

 			       COMPILING

$ git clone https://github.com/mrclksr/dsbmc-cli.git
$ git clone https://github.com/mrclksr/libdsbmc.git
$ cd dsbmc-cli && make

				USAGE

Usage: dsbmc-cli -m|-u|-e|-s dev
       dsbmc-cli -v speed dev
       dsbmc-cli -l

Flags
-m	Mount
-u	Unmount
-v	Set CD/DVD reading speed
-e	Eject media
-s	Query media size.
-l	List available devices.

